Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{=22}===============================DIALOGUE============================
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.85,0:02:17.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê?! Ah...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.31,0:02:24.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Seus idiotas!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.87,0:02:27.06,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,A culpa é de vocês que ele escapou!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.06,0:02:29.53,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ele era nossa galinha dos ovos de ouro!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.87,0:02:35.11,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Saiam do caminho!\NNão pensem que a gente não vai prender todos vocês!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.11,0:02:38.68,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que vocês estão fazendo, Marinheiros?!\NNão interrompam o Soul King!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.68,0:02:41.11,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ei, o que tá acontecendo lá dentro?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.11,0:02:42.85,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tá um tumulto!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.85,0:02:46.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Os Marinheiros invadiram de repente\Npra prender o Soul King,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.28,0:02:50.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,mas ele escapou porque\Nos fãs bloquearam os perseguidores!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.39,0:02:53.76,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Droga! Aquele traidor...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.36,0:02:56.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Isso mesmo! Essa é uma grande notícia!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.39,0:02:59.26,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O músico Brook faz parte\Nda tripulação do Chapéu de Palha!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.26,0:03:00.76,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ele na verdade é um pirata!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.67,0:03:11.74,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Muito obrigado!\NIsso é que é ter timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.74,0:03:16.58,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,A Shakky-nee me mandou! Seus amigos\Ndevem estar esperando no Grove 42!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.58,0:03:20.08,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Faz tempo! Meu coração tá\Ncheio de expectativa!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.08,0:03:23.22,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ah, eu não tenho um coração pra encher.
Comment: 0,0:03:28.66,0:03:29.56,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.56,0:03:30.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\i1}Isso mesmo!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.69,0:03:33.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\i1}Os Marinheiros estão se movendo,\Ne o Luffy tá na área!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.63,0:03:38.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\i1}Estamos levando o {\i0}Sunny{\i1} pro Grove 42,\Nentão nos vemos lá!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.10,0:03:39.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Entendido.
Comment: 0,0:03:39.24,0:03:39.94,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Clank.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.94,0:03:40.74,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que foi isso?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.74,0:03:42.47,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, você não tava ouvindo?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.47,0:03:44.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Como eu posso dizer...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.88,0:03:50.61,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Marinheiros. Vindo. Nós. Navio. Fugir.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.18,0:03:52.15,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Entendeu?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.15,0:03:55.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu entenderia melhor se você falasse normalmente!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.69,0:03:59.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Mas frases completas são difíceis pra cabeça-dura.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.49,0:04:00.29,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.96,0:04:05.26,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tá bom. Você. Depois. Cortado.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.26,0:04:06.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tá, tá.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.66,0:04:08.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Aliás, você tá ouvindo esse barulho?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.90,0:04:09.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hã?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.17,0:04:14.84,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,De fato. Lá. Barulho.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.35,0:04:25.58,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Calem a boca, todos vocês!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.19,0:04:31.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,A gente encontrou\Num dos culpados...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.36,0:04:33.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,que ousou me desrespeitar!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.06,0:04:37.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Esse cara!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.39,0:04:37.09,Secondary-207+,,0,0,0,,Hã?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.09,0:04:40.23,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vou começar dando uma lição {\i1}nesse{\i0} cara!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.23,0:04:44.23,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ele vai aprender a não mexer comigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.23,0:04:47.37,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,E o que eu vou fazer com ele...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.37,0:04:50.81,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,vai servir de aviso pra cada\Num de vocês!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.81,0:04:54.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Se mexer comigo, é assim\Nque você vai acabar!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.65,0:04:56.78,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Entenderam, seus vermes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.22,0:05:01.95,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Um cara com uma recompensa de\N400 milhões de belly é assustador mesmo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.95,0:05:03.85,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Qual é o problema desse cara?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.85,0:05:06.56,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Zoro, Sanji, vocês conhecem ele?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.56,0:05:07.12,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hã?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.12,0:05:08.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É que, antes...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.86,0:05:12.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Fim da linha, piratas!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.10,0:05:17.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Chapéu de Palha Luffy e todos os seus\Nseguidores, se rendam agora!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.63,0:05:18.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O-Os Marinheiros...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.87,0:05:23.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Bloqueamos todas as saídas do Grove 46!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.07,0:05:24.98,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não tem como escapar agora!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.58,0:05:28.38,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,C... Como os Marinheiros descobriram sobre mim?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.61,0:05:30.95,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que você quer dizer com isso?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.95,0:05:33.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, Capitão! Estamos cercados!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.55,0:05:35.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não entre em pânico, idiota!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.72,0:05:37.96,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Pra que você acha que a gente\Nrecrutou esses membros novos?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.96,0:05:40.12,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Alguns deles valem mais de 100 milhões!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.12,0:05:41.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Mas a gente tá em desvantagem numérica...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.49,0:05:42.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Fica olhando, imbecil!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.36,0:05:46.06,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, Caribou!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.06,0:05:48.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Usa aquele Marinheiro de escudo pra abrir caminho!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.47,0:05:50.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ele disse "Marinheiro"...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.63,0:05:54.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Parece que capturaram um dos nossos batedores!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.27,0:05:55.44,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Droga, isso não é bom!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.91,0:05:57.67,Secondary-207+,,0,0,0,,O que você tá fazendo, Caribou?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.67,0:06:00.51,Secondary-207+,,0,0,0,,Usar ele é nosso passaporte pra sair daqui!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.08,0:06:06.62,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu não posso fazer isso, Chefão!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.82,0:06:06.62,Secondary-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.12,0:06:09.62,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Porque esse soldado mentiu...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.62,0:06:13.26,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ele disse que ainda não tinha chamado os Marinheiros!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.86,0:06:15.76,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não faça isso!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.84,0:06:28.44,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Aquele maluco ignorou minha ordem!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.27,0:06:31.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eita, ele fez mesmo...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.11,0:06:37.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eles parecem seguir uma regra suja\Nque permite mentir pros inimigos!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.65,0:06:39.68,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Cara, que coisa mais desagradável!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.08,0:06:44.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Então nenhum de vocês\Ntem intenção de se render!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.89,0:06:46.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Atrás deles! Peguem os piratas!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.76,0:06:53.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Idiotas! Nosso chefe vale 400 milhões!\NEle é o Chapéu de Palha Luffy, sabia?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.50,0:06:55.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Pode vir!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.90,0:07:00.77,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,A situação tá feia, Capitão. Vamos fugir!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.77,0:07:03.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ingratos! Obedeçam o capitão!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.01,0:07:06.84,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hã? Por que estão me chamando de "chefe"?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.84,0:07:09.61,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,De novo, o que você quer dizer com isso?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.06,0:07:23.73,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não se assustem! Vamos!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.96,0:07:26.03,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você é...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.76,0:07:30.83,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,o que vale 88 milhões,\NLip "Service" Doughty!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.30,0:07:34.74,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu simplesmente adoro seu jeito de lutar.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.74,0:07:36.94,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não se assustem! Preparem-se pra atirar!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.21,0:07:44.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ele tem uma recompensa de 92 milhões...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.28,0:07:46.98,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Albion, "o Mutilado"!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.32,0:07:52.42,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não recuem! Lutem pela justiça!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.42,0:07:53.42,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– É!\N– É!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.83,0:08:00.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O sangue dos hipócritas fede demais!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.00,0:08:03.47,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Uma recompensa de 210 milhões...\NO pirata "Cabelo Molhado" Caribou!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.87,0:08:05.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Se renda agora!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.07,0:08:09.37,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Espera... você comeu uma fruta do diabo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.54,0:08:13.81,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você não devia ter feito isso!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.81,0:08:16.18,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não faz bem se forçar demais!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.32,0:08:19.28,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,Minha espada...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.02,0:08:25.02,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,U-Uau! O que tá acontecendo agora?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.02,0:08:26.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Pacifista!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.72,0:08:27.42,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.16,0:08:36.93,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Por que as armas humanas dos Marinheiros estão aqui?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.47,0:08:41.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,São aqueles caras parecidos com o Kuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.14,0:08:43.61,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Mas a Hancock disse pra eu não causar problemas...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.61,0:08:47.91,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sério, que diabos você\Nquer dizer com isso?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.32,0:08:56.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Pirata Chapéu de Palha Luffy: Confirmado.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.69,0:09:00.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,São pacifistas de verdade?\NE estão atirando em mim?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.26,0:09:04.73,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Pacifista, é? Que emocionante!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.67,0:09:16.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Recompensa de 88 milhões de belly,\NLip "Service" Doughty: Neutralizado.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.21,0:09:18.08,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Capitão Doughty!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.84,0:09:24.18,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sigam o pacifista! Capturem os piratas!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.18,0:09:25.02,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– É!\N– É!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.02,0:09:26.62,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Com um tiro só...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.62,0:09:29.52,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Mesmo com uma recompensa de 88 milhões,\Nele não teve chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.52,0:09:32.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Isso não é bo– O quê...?!\NCapitão, aonde você vai?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.69,0:09:34.42,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Espere por mim!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.76,0:09:34.42,Secondary-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, ei!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.42,0:09:38.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Idiotas! Ele destruiu o Doughty,\Nentão não temos chance! Melhor fugir!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.43,0:09:47.17,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Chefe Chapéu de Palha, faça alguma coisa!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.14,0:09:52.31,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Desse jeito, essas armas humanas\Nvão acabar com todos nós!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.31,0:09:54.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Chefão...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.48,0:09:55.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hã?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.35,0:09:57.45,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O Chefão sumiu!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.45,0:09:59.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Chefão?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.08,0:10:01.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eles estão falando do Chapéu de Palha?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.45,0:10:04.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Espera! Meu lado tá doendo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.72,0:10:07.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Seus idiotas...! Fujam, ou eles vão matar–
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.83,0:10:10.56,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você tá no caminho, idiota!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.96,0:10:13.13,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hã? Quem é você?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.70,0:10:17.97,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Esse é...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.97,0:10:20.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O Chefão!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.64,0:10:27.44,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Por que você tá se passando pelo Chapéu de Palha?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.44,0:10:31.78,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,E-E-Ei, seu bastardo!\NVocê sabe quem eu sou?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.78,0:10:35.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sai da frente, ou eu vou arrancar\Nsuas tripas até você morrer!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.69,0:10:40.86,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Isso pode te surpreender, mas eu sou\No filho de Dragon, o Revolucionário!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.86,0:10:43.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,E neto de Garp, o Herói!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.59,0:10:48.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu sou um pirata de primeira com uma\Nrecompensa de 400 milhões de belly, Chapéu de–
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.54,0:10:55.17,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Um lixo como você não pode ser o Chapéu de Palha!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.94,0:10:58.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.71,0:10:59.68,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hã?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.68,0:11:00.88,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ah...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.88,0:11:02.85,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– O quê?!\N– O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.81,0:11:07.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Chefe Chapéu de Palha...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.08,0:11:09.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Agora eu entendo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.55,0:11:13.92,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Todos foram enganados e entraram\Npra uma tripulação falsa do Chapéu de Palha.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.92,0:11:16.26,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,PX-5, quem é esse cara de verdade?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.40,0:11:23.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Pirata "Três Línguas" Demaro Black.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.63,0:11:26.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Recompensa: 26 milhões de belly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.14,0:11:27.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– O quê?!\N– O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.00,0:11:29.47,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vinte e seis milhões? Isso quer dizer que ele é...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.57,0:11:32.58,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– ...um impostor?!\N– ...um impostor?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.41,0:11:36.11,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eles descobriram! Foge!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.31,0:11:39.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Esse cara é sério?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.28,0:11:43.45,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Então ele se passou pelo Chapéu de Palha\NLuffy e enganou a gente!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.45,0:11:45.62,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Porque o verdadeiro morreu!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.62,0:11:51.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Droga! Quase fui enganado por um fracote\Ncom uma recompensa mísera de 26 milhões!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.36,0:11:52.13,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.93,0:11:55.77,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Aquele cara tava fingindo ser eu?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.77,0:11:57.37,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Então, o Sanji e o Zoro também?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.37,0:12:00.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eles eram igualzinhos aos verdadeiros!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.64,0:12:03.54,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É melhor eu ir embora antes que algo mais aconteça.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.11,0:12:09.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Esse impostor é um idiota,\Nmas vocês também deram azar.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.05,0:12:11.68,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Estão todos presos!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.95,0:12:18.56,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,E por acaso o verdadeiro\NChapéu de Palha também tá aqui.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.52,0:12:23.96,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O PX-5 detectou ele quando entramos nessa área.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.96,0:12:26.43,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Acabe com ele, PX-5!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.24,0:12:38.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Essa foi por pouco!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.21,0:12:42.41,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que você tá fazendo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.41,0:12:45.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Essa bolsa tem todos os meus preciosos almoços!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.85,0:12:50.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O... O rosto dele...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.06,0:12:58.13,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– É igualzinho ao cartaz!\N– É igualzinho ao cartaz!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.83,0:13:03.97,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Aquele cara é o verdadeiro Chapéu de Palha!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.97,0:13:05.44,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Firmes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.44,0:13:08.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,A gente veio aqui pra pegar o verdadeiro mesmo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.27,0:13:09.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– Sim, senhor!\N– Sim, senhor!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.01,0:13:10.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Chapéu de Palha!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.21,0:13:13.68,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê?! Vai tentar\Nme parar de novo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.24,0:13:17.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu tenho que evitar problemas\Npra poder zarpar!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.71,0:13:20.92,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não se preocupe! Você não vai precisar zarpar!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.35,0:13:25.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Diferente de dois anos atrás, agora eu sou\Noficialmente um membro da Marinha!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.82,0:13:28.06,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Então é aqui que eu te capturo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.49,0:13:29.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,PX-5!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.53,0:13:38.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Bem devagar...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.87,0:13:43.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.91,0:13:50.81,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Gear Second!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.05,0:13:58.42,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Gomu Gomu no...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.53,0:14:10.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Jet Pistol!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.41,0:14:18.88,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Chapéu de Palha...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.04,0:14:22.11,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ele tá usando Haki!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.95,0:14:28.42,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– Ele derrotou o pacifista com um golpe só!\N– Ele derrotou o pacifista com um golpe só!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.59,0:14:37.83,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Até mais!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.83,0:14:40.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Aposto que a gente se encontra de novo por aí!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.70,0:14:42.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Espere, Chapéu de Palha!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.10,0:14:44.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não deixem o Chapéu de Palha escapar!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.30,0:14:45.54,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– É!\N– É!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.64,0:14:49.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.67,0:14:50.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Opa?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.57,0:14:53.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Luffy! Eu sabia que era você!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.01,0:14:56.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Por que você sempre se mete em confusão?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.51,0:14:58.38,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ohhh!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.38,0:15:03.22,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sem erro dessa vez! Faz tempo, galera!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.22,0:15:06.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Roronoa! Perna Negra! Então eles tão vivos?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.99,0:15:08.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,PX-7!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.93,0:15:18.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– Sai da frente!\N– Sai da frente!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.34,0:15:25.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu cortei ele!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.64,0:15:28.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não, eu quebrei o pescoço dele!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.11,0:15:33.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,São os Chapéu de Palha! Os {\i1}verdadeiros{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.28,0:15:36.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eles não têm nada a ver com os impostores!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.56,0:15:43.73,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, Luffy, você é o nono.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.73,0:15:45.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Cala a boca! Para de se gabar por isso!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.90,0:15:48.33,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vamos, Luffy! Todo mundo tá no navio!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.33,0:15:49.17,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tá bom!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.90,0:15:54.44,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não deixem eles escaparem!\NCapturem a qualquer custo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.44,0:15:55.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– Sim, senhor!\N– Sim, senhor!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.24,0:16:00.18,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Faz muito tempo mesmo!\NSeria como todo mundo tá!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.18,0:16:01.85,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tô tão feliz!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.39,0:16:10.85,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, o que houve?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.89,0:16:14.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.03,0:16:19.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Rayleigh!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.00,0:16:20.56,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.56,0:16:22.23,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não pode ser!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.17,0:16:24.97,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Rei Sombrio Rayleigh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.71,0:16:32.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vim ver como você tava,\Nmas parece que tá tudo bem.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.38,0:16:36.25,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você refinou suas habilidades ainda mais.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.25,0:16:37.31,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Aham!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.71,0:16:41.22,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Agora vai! Seus amigos estão esperando.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.22,0:16:46.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Aham! Rayleigh, muito obrigado\Npor tudo nesses dois anos!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.06,0:16:51.26,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Isso não combina com você. Só vai!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.70,0:17:01.47,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Rayleigh!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.17,0:17:05.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu vou conseguir!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.48,0:17:15.32,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu vou me tornar o Rei dos Piratas!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.36,0:17:29.73,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que vocês tão fazendo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.73,0:17:31.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Peguem o Chapéu de Palha logo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.50,0:17:33.54,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Opa!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.54,0:17:35.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Anda logo, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.27,0:17:37.17,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Rayleigh, obrigado por tudo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.17,0:17:39.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Então, Rayleigh...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.04,0:17:42.41,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Obrigado mais uma vez por tudo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.41,0:17:45.18,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu tô indo agora!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.72,0:17:50.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.54,0:18:09.97,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eles foram por ali!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.97,0:18:11.91,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– Atrás deles!\N– Não deixem eles escaparem!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.51,0:18:16.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Cheguem ao topo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.65,0:18:23.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Os Chapéu de Palha estão indo pro Grove 42!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.79,0:18:25.86,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não deixem eles escaparem!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.33,0:18:31.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que foi isso?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.00,0:18:36.17,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Rei Sombrio Rayleigh!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.17,0:18:38.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É um novo começo pro meu pupilo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.50,0:18:40.37,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não pegue pesado demais com ele.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.24,0:18:45.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Q-O que é essa linha?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.38,0:18:49.31,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu não recomendo cruzá-la.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.68,0:18:58.12,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ah, bolsas de bolha! Tem um monte!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.12,0:18:59.52,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que tem dentro delas?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.52,0:19:05.76,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Estão cheias de comida. Imagino que o estômago\Nde todo mundo cresceu nesses dois anos.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.76,0:19:07.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Depois eu deixo vocês se encherem!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.90,0:19:11.13,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sério?! Mal posso esperar pra comer sua comida!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.13,0:19:13.47,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ali estão eles! Por aqui!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.97,0:19:16.91,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Opa? Eles deram a volta!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.17,0:19:19.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não tem jeito, né?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.71,0:19:21.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Todo mundo, avançar!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.71,0:19:22.85,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– É!\N– É!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.15,0:19:29.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu quero... virar uma pulga...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.69,0:19:31.22,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que houve? O que você...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.22,0:19:33.22,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu quero virar um ácaro...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.22,0:19:34.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.69,0:19:36.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Que diabos...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.66,0:19:42.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu... eu...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.23,0:19:45.84,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu quero virar um piolho...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.84,0:19:47.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.14,0:19:48.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Deve ser...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.67,0:19:53.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Como eu suspeitava,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.64,0:19:55.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,essa confusão é obra de {\i1}vocês{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.25,0:19:58.85,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não acredito nisso!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.15,0:20:03.52,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vocês ainda não foram embora!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.52,0:20:06.92,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É mesmo! Eu me lembro de você de Thriller Bark!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.59,0:20:08.83,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ela era...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.83,0:20:11.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que você ainda tá fazendo aqui?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.99,0:20:15.93,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você devia ser mais gentil com quem\Nte trouxe de volta pra essa ilha!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.93,0:20:18.17,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Se eu não tivesse te guiado, você estaria...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.90,0:20:22.41,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Pelo menos tenha um pouco de gratid–
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.41,0:20:23.81,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Sniff, sniff...}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.81,0:20:26.54,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Uma mulher de verdade! Uma mulher de verdade!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.54,0:20:29.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É claro que eu sou! O quê,\Nvocê tá maluco da cabeça?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.01,0:20:31.58,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Enfim, zarpe logo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.58,0:20:33.68,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu vi alguns navios da Marinha por aqui!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.68,0:20:34.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– O quê?\N– O quê?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.18,0:20:37.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Logo não vai ter saída!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.46,0:20:43.53,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Oh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.53,0:20:44.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Essa voz...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.69,0:20:49.43,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Usopp! Nami! Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.43,0:20:52.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,♪ Frrranky! ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.11,0:20:57.91,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Brook!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.91,0:21:00.91,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei! Não acredito que você largou o estrelato!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.91,0:21:01.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Esse é o cara!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.15,0:21:07.02,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Faz muito tempo, galera!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.02,0:21:10.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vocês duas ficaram ainda mais bonitas!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.59,0:21:14.92,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Bom, Nami...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.36,0:21:16.86,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,já faz dois anos, então...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.83,0:21:21.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ah, você vai cantar pra gente?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.54,0:21:28.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,...você seria tão gentil\Nde me mostrar sua calci–
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.00,0:21:29.81,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que {\i1}você{\i0} acha?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.81,0:21:32.88,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu nunca deixei você ver dois anos atrás também!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.88,0:21:36.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,E-Eu tô tão animado em te ver de novo... Olha?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.21,0:21:39.98,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tá... fazendo meu coração estremecer. Embora...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.98,0:21:44.25,Secondary-207+,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Eu não tenha um coração que possa estremecer...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.72,0:21:44.25,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei...! O astro do rock tá tendo convulsões.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.25,0:21:48.32,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Francamente! Nenhum de vocês amadureceu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.49,0:21:50.73,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Aliás...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.43,0:21:54.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Parece que faltam alguns membros.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.70,0:21:58.17,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ah, é verdade. O Chopper foi buscar eles–
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.87,0:21:58.63,Secondary-207+,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ei!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.17,0:21:58.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– Hã?\N– Hã?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.81,0:22:07.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Finalmente chegaram!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.48,0:22:10.08,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Uau, ei!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.98,0:22:14.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Todo mundo!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.59,0:22:18.92,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu encontrei eles!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.42,0:22:23.43,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Luffy! Zoro! Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.43,0:22:25.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.63,0:22:31.43,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Luffy! Senti tanto sua falta!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.43,0:22:34.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vocês tão com cara de mais homens!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.74,0:22:38.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Estamos todos juntos de novo!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.51,0:22:43.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Finalmente–
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.35,0:22:44.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.21,0:22:46.62,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Galera!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.12,0:22:57.29,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.06,0:23:00.23,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.57,0:23:08.54,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Bom, então, obrigado!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.54,0:23:10.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Manda um oi pra todo mundo no Reino Birdie!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.61,0:23:14.81,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Usopp! O Sanji tá bem?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.81,0:23:18.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Uma... Uma... Uma mulher bonita...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.01,0:23:20.52,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, fica comigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.91,0:23:20.52,Secondary-207+,,0,0,0,,Duas mulheres bonitas...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.52,0:23:23.32,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Chopper, isso é muito sério!\NPrecisamos estancar o sangue!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.02,0:23:27.96,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,F-F-Franky, você tá...!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.96,0:23:29.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Qual o problema?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.59,0:23:33.76,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tem algo que te preocupa-{\fnFOT-KafuTechno Std E Strp\i1\b1}mecha{\fn\i0\b0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.30,0:23:37.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,"Mecha"?! Eu também quero brincar!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.23,0:23:37.20,Secondary-207+,,0,0,0,,Espera, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.97,0:23:39.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Deixa essa besteira pra depois!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.64,0:23:42.97,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Parece que os navios da Marinha já chegaram!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.88,0:23:48.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não! Quando eles chegaram?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.28,0:23:52.42,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Três navios da Marinha!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.58,0:23:58.29,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, a gente luta?!\NEles tão se aproximando!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.29,0:24:01.22,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Fogo! Mandem eles pro fundo!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.73,0:24:05.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Slave...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.46,0:24:07.13,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Arrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.50,0:24:15.44,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê...? O que acabou de acontecer?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.44,0:24:17.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,I-Isso é...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.54,0:24:22.58,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,As Piratas Kuja!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.91,0:24:26.22,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Quem...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.92,0:24:30.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,colocou um navio da Marinha...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.95,0:24:34.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,no meu caminho?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.40,0:24:44.37,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Esse é o emblema Kuja!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.37,0:24:45.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,As "Kuja"?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.87,0:24:50.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,São piratas Amazonas poderosas lideradas\Npela Imperatriz Pirata, uma dos Warlords.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.71,0:24:52.11,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Uma Warlord?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.11,0:24:54.18,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,A Imperatriz Boa Hancock.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.18,0:25:00.25,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Dizem que quem a vê fica enfeitiçado\Ne se transforma em pedra.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.25,0:25:03.32,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ai, que brilhante! Ela é deslumbrante!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.32,0:25:05.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,A beleza dela não tem fim!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.69,0:25:08.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não tavam exagerando! Ela é uma deusa!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.26,0:25:10.86,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Deusa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.86,0:25:11.83,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Onde ela tá?!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.83,0:25:13.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Deusa? Deusa?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.16,0:25:18.03,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Deusa... Ah, deusa... Ah, deusa... D... D... Deusa...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.77,0:25:20.37,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ele virou pedra!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.17,0:25:23.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, são a Hancock e as piratas dela!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.01,0:25:23.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– Hã?\N– Hã?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.57,0:25:27.31,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Mova seu navio, Boa Hancock!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.31,0:25:29.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não interfira na nossa missão!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.71,0:25:34.98,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Parem com essas acusações sem fundamento! Eu só\Nnão tô a fim de sair do caminho.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.98,0:25:37.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,E-Ela tá agindo como uma criança!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.65,0:25:38.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Algum problema com isso?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.89,0:25:44.06,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,Vai, Luffy... Eu abri caminho pra você!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.86,0:25:48.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ela acabou de piscar pra gente...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.70,0:25:51.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ela nos ajudou. Vamos zarpar agora!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.07,0:25:52.94,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você conhece aquela Warlord?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.94,0:25:57.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É... Eu fui mandado pra Ilha das Mulheres\Ne fiz amizade com elas.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.64,0:26:00.81,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não é a lendária ilha das mulheres?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.81,0:26:02.08,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ela existe de verdade?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.68,0:26:05.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você é amigo da Imperatriz Pirata?!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.51,0:26:09.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei! Você pelo menos treinou direito?!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.89,0:26:11.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É, tô pronto!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.05,0:26:14.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Droga... Não é justo...! Não é justo...!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.89,0:26:16.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que foi, Sanji?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.36,0:26:20.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Uau, então eles são os amigos do Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.40,0:26:23.83,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tem um monte de criaturas\Nque eu nunca vi antes.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.83,0:26:26.47,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– Um, dois, três, quatro...\N– Parece que eles tão se divertindo!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.17,0:26:30.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tá bom, vamos nos preparar pra zarpar!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.14,0:26:31.91,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– É!\N– Sim, Nami-swan!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.91,0:26:34.94,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hã? Qual o problema, Usopp?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.94,0:26:39.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É que... Vocês derrotaram\Ntodos aqueles Marinheiros?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.05,0:26:43.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não. A gente ainda podia ouvir eles\Ngritando enquanto a gente voava.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.62,0:26:47.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Então por que eles não tão\Nvindo atrás da gente por terra?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.43,0:26:57.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Aqui é o Pelotão de Reforço 3!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.67,0:26:58.77,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tá me ouvindo?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.00,0:27:01.97,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}O que houve? O que aconteceu?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.97,0:27:04.61,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não conseguimos chegar no Grove 42!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.61,0:27:05.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Por que não?!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.71,0:27:07.74,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,P-Porque...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.74,0:27:10.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,tem insetos gigantes bloqueando nosso caminho!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.55,0:27:12.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}O quê? Insetos?!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.92,0:27:16.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que são essas coisas?!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.42,0:27:21.76,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Fogo!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.20,0:27:33.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu não vou deixar eles atrapalharem\Na nova aventura do Usopp'n!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.67,0:27:39.44,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Quando homens se separam, não derramamos lágrimas'n.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.54,0:27:43.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Boa sorte, Usopp'n!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.11,0:27:47.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Se eles não tão vindo, ótimo.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.55,0:27:50.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O problema deles é nossa sorte.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.05,0:27:52.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vamos embora logo!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.35,0:27:54.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Nami, mostre o caminho!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.72,0:27:55.52,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Deixa comigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.56,0:27:58.33,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Beleza!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.83,0:28:02.03,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Aqui é o Pelotão 4.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.03,0:28:03.77,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Me desculpe.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.77,0:28:07.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Fomos pegos por uma chuva repentina e a pólvora molhou!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.10,0:28:08.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Chuva? Onde tá chovendo?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.80,0:28:10.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Chuva? Onde tá chovendo?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.14,0:28:14.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sabaody Archipelago deveria estar\Ncom céu limpo e sol hoje!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.95,0:28:19.78,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sem trovão.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.78,0:28:23.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Queremos evitar machucar civis.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.05,0:28:26.06,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,As bolhas daqui são um saco...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.06,0:28:29.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Mas é difícil acreditar que\Npegamos um vento tão perfeito.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.66,0:28:32.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Nos trouxe direitinho pro Sabaody Archipelago.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.60,0:28:36.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É porque a Nami é uma expert nisso.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.10,0:28:45.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Boa sorte! Vamos sentir saudades\Ndaqui de Weatheria!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.42,0:29:03.73,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Oh, tá inflando!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.66,0:29:08.53,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê? Essa geleia infla?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.07,0:29:15.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Oh, ganhamos um teto de bolha!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.74,0:29:16.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ouçam, todos.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.44,0:29:22.18,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Um navio revestido consegue suportar\Nqualquer tipo de pressão.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.18,0:29:27.68,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Quando o Franky remover a bolsa de flutuação\Nque sustenta a quilha do navio,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.68,0:29:31.62,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,o revestimento do {\i1}Sunny{\i0} vai fazê-lo começar a afundar.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.62,0:29:32.62,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É assim que funciona.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.62,0:29:34.22,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– Entendi.\N– Entendi.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.22,0:29:35.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Complicado demais, né?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.69,0:29:37.83,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Enfim, baixem a vela agora!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.83,0:29:38.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– A vela?\N– A vela?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.66,0:29:42.83,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Em vez do vento, são as correntes marítimas\Nque movem um navio revestido.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.83,0:29:45.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Então ele não só afunda até o destino.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.54,0:29:49.37,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Certo! Vamos logo antes de encontrar\Nmais Marinheiros!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.71,0:29:54.08,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Aqui é o Pelotão Central 5 no Grove 42!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.08,0:29:55.74,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Temos uma emergência!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.74,0:29:59.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,As tropas que chegaram antes de nós,\No Pelotão 2, parecem ter ficado negativos!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.65,0:30:01.78,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Do que você tá falando? "Negativos"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.78,0:30:03.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu quero virar musgo...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.05,0:30:05.85,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu sou inútil. Quero virar uma pulga d'água...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.85,0:30:10.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Segundo eles, o Chapéu de Palha Luffy\Nsubiu num pássaro gigante e voou embora!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.63,0:30:13.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Pássaro? O que vocês tão fazendo agora?!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.20,0:30:16.03,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Estamos lutando contra inimigos desconhecidos!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.20,0:30:20.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Reforços da Marinha!\NEra pra gente já ter saído...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.87,0:30:22.74,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Todo mundo!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.74,0:30:27.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O navio do Chapéu de Palha está no alcance agora!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.51,0:30:31.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Espera! Um pássaro gigante\Ntá vindo na nossa direção!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.49,0:30:42.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É ele!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.53,0:30:45.86,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eles estão atrás da gente!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.86,0:30:47.16,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Deixa comigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.77,0:30:51.10,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,E aí, Nami?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.10,0:30:53.30,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,Por favor, olha pra mim...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.30,0:30:55.80,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,Veja o quanto eu fiquei mais forte.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.80,0:30:58.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.54,0:31:03.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Respondam, Pelotão 5! O que tá acontecendo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.55,0:31:05.61,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}N-Nós estamos...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.61,0:31:10.25,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Estamos enfrentando... um obstáculo inesperado...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.25,0:31:11.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não faça isso!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.22,0:31:18.26,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Como vocês ousam nos rejeitar assim?!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.26,0:31:20.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Talvez eles sejam todos tímidos.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.70,0:31:23.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vocês não precisam ter vergonha!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.20,0:31:27.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vamos tomar um chá juntos!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.90,0:31:31.81,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,E-Eu tô ficando... tô ficando maluco, né?!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.44,0:31:38.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Oh! Que rostinho mais fofo!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.21,0:31:39.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não, não faça isso!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.25,0:31:44.92,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}O que houve? Respondam, Pelotão 5!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.76,0:31:49.02,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,Sanji-kins, agora é sua chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.46,0:31:53.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, ei, o que houve, Sanji?!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.06,0:32:00.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,E-E-Eu não sei... De repente, senti como\Nse alguém tivesse apertado meu coração...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.24,0:32:01.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Removi a bolsa de flutuação!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.87,0:32:04.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tá bom! E a vela?!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.04,0:32:06.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Prontos quando quiser!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.91,0:32:08.41,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tá na hora de ir, Nami?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.41,0:32:10.41,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sim, ao seu comando, Capitão.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.75,0:32:18.92,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Certo...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.43,0:32:25.13,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Galera!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.26,0:32:31.23,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu tenho tanta coisa que quero\Ncontar pra vocês, mas antes de tudo,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.23,0:32:35.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,obrigado por aceitarem minha decisão\Negoísta por dois anos!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.24,0:32:38.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não é como se fosse a primeira vez.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.04,0:32:41.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ele tem razão! Você sempre foi assim!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.81,0:32:49.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Contra-Almirante, o navio pirata tá submergindo!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.72,0:32:51.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê?! Maldição!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.72,0:32:53.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Desgraçados!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.09,0:32:54.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vocês têm ideia...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.99,0:32:57.56,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,de quão perigosos esses piratas são? Ei!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.56,0:32:58.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Contra-Almirante!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.96,0:33:02.53,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,Se cuida, Luffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.40,0:33:07.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Baixem a vela!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.57,0:33:08.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– Sim!\N– É!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.41,0:33:19.41,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Zarpar!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.41,0:33:21.78,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– É!\N– É!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.29,0:33:32.29,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vamos pra Ilha dos Homens-Peixe!
